stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE
    
    IDLE --> ENTRY_ZONE: entry_zone
    
    ENTRY_ZONE --> ENTRY_ZONE: any_token_fired && entry_zone<br/>[Calculate EP/SL]
    ENTRY_ZONE --> ENTERING: place_order_zone && got_token<br/>[Place buy order]
    ENTRY_ZONE --> RESET_ZONE: reset_zone
    ENTRY_ZONE --> RESET_ZONE: level_is_broken<br/>[Cancel orders, reset params]
    
    ENTERING --> IN_TRADE: in_trade_zone<br/>[Place exit orders,<br/>record entry bar,<br/>init chandelier]
    ENTERING --> ENTERING: !in_trade_zone<br/>[Wait for trade open]
    ENTERING --> RESET_ZONE: level_is_broken<br/>[Cancel orders, reset params]
    
    IN_TRADE --> IN_TRADE: enable_trailing<br/>[Recalculate dynamic SL,<br/>update exit orders]
    IN_TRADE --> EXIT: date_exit<br/>[Date-based exit]
    IN_TRADE --> EXIT: ch_stop<br/>[Chandelier exit]
    IN_TRADE --> EXIT: trade_closed
    
    EXIT --> IDLE: [Send notification,<br/>reset all params]
    
    RESET_ZONE --> IDLE: [Cancel orders,<br/>reset all params]
    
    TERMINATE --> TERMINATE: [Needs reconfiguration]
    
    note right of IDLE
        Waiting for entry zone
    end note
    
    note right of ENTRY_ZONE
        Waiting for token signal
        Calculating entry params
    end note
    
    note right of ENTERING
        Order placed,
        waiting for fill
    end note
    
    note right of IN_TRADE
        Active trade monitoring:
        - Dynamic stop loss
        - Exit signals
        - Trailing stops
    end note
    
    note right of EXIT
        Trade completed,
        cleanup and reporting
    end note
    
    note right of TERMINATE
        Reserved for unrecoverable or manual reconfiguration states
    end note
    
    note left of IDLE
        📋 KEY FEATURES:
        • 7 distinct states with clear purposes
        • Transitions with conditions
        • Actions in brackets show what happens
        • Self-loops for waiting/recalculating
        • TERMINATE requires manual intervention
        
        🎯 NOTABLE PATTERNS:
        • Happy path: IDLE → ENTRY_ZONE → 
          ENTERING → IN_TRADE → EXIT → IDLE
        • Safety exits to RESET_ZONE & TERMINATE
        • IN_TRADE has continuous monitoring loop
        
        ✅ ARCHITECTURE:
        • Clear separation of concerns
        • One "dead end" state (TERMINATE)
        • Linear flow with proper cleanup paths
    end note